snippet.title: Theatre of Doom - Steam Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Theatre of Doom on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/553020/

Theatre of Doom is an intense and fast top-down action game. Fight your way through the hellish stages against demonic marionette puppets, and ferocious monsters.

Games reviews and download: http://download.online-games.co/
